Here's some help about how you can use FileFix to change your fileareas.

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
%list		list of fileareas avialable
%help		what are you reading, pal? :)
%unlinked       list of unlinked fileareas
%linked         list of linked fileareas
%query          the same
%avail          list all fileareas that are available at this system's uplinks
%pause          stop recieve files
%resume         recieved files again
%resend <file>
    <filearea>  recieved file from filearea
+<echotag>	subscribe filearea (support mask)
<echotag>	the same
-<echotag>	unsubscribe filearea

attention!	all other lines are *ignored*
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-


