 Msg  : 5 of 8                             Pvt
 From : Your Name                          2:5020/960.1    13 Feb 99  19:51:12
 To   : FileFix                            2:5020/960      15 Feb 99  21:57:42
 Subj : PASSWORD              <- Your password
